test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [86] == [-86, -86, -8...-86, -86, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 86 != -86
  Right contains 6 more items, first extra item: -86
  Full diff:
  - [-86, -86, -86, -86, -86, -86, -86]
  + [86]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [86] == [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 86 != 0
  Right contains 6 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
  + [86]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [86] == [7482, 7568, ...0, 7826, 7912]
  At index 0 diff: 86 != 7482
  Right contains 5 more items, first extra item: 7568
  Full diff:
  - [7482, 7568, 7654, 7740, 7826, 7912]
  + [86]
